data.description:
DREAM BIG!!
Welcome to your dream home! This beautiful 3BR 1.5BA rowhome, located just off Loch Raven Boulevard, offers the perfect blend of comfort and style.
This home is a true gem, with a roof that was replaced in 2020, ensuring peace of mind and energy efficiency. The open dining and kitchen floor plan is perfect for entertaining, and the remodeled kitchen with stainless steel appliances is a chef's delight. The original hardwood floors add character and warmth to the space.
With a finished basement, you'll have extra space for a family room, home office, or gym. Step outside to the deck and enjoy the fresh air and relaxation in your private outdoor oasis. Plus, the convenience of two parking pad spaces is a rare find in this area.
Don't miss this opportunity to make this lovely rowhome your own!
